column1: SA25 Total Full-Time and Part-Time Employment by SIC Industry 1/

1/ The estimates of employment for 1969-74 are based on the 1967 Standard Industrial Classification (SIC). The estimates for 1975-87 are based on the 1972 SIC. The estimates for 1988-2001 are based on the 1987 SIC.
Last updated: May 30, 2014-- revised estimates for 1969-2001.
